prop_short_description: Live in luxury in the heart of Chicago's South Loop neighborhood.
prop_long_description: 1000 South Clark is a luxury apartment building offering studio, one, two, and three-bedroom apartment homes in Chicago's South Loop neighborhood. With breathtaking views of the city skyline, Lake Michigan, and Grant Park, our apartments feature floor-to-ceiling windows, balconies, gourmet kitchens with stainless steel appliances, in-unit washer and dryers, and spacious closets. Our community amenities include a rooftop terrace with a pool, fitness center, resident lounge, dog park, and more. 1000 South Clark is the perfect home for those who want to experience luxury living in the heart of the city.
